          "description": "This unit is a Stun Absorber. Whenever any ally would be affected by stun, this unit takes the stun instead.\n\nIf this unit takes damage from an attack while it does not have Endure and survives until after the end of the turn, this unit will Endure the next damage that would defeat it with 1HP. Endure effects cannot stack.\n\nThis unit gains the Armor status effect at the very start of the battle if it is on the battlefield. Armor grants 50% damage reduction from the next attack, then the effect is removed."
